3. Legal basis: Marriage Interpretation (I) Article 5 (Refund when no registration exists).
4. Factors for adjustment: Short cohabitation duration, defendant's pregnancy termination (physical damage), and common expenses.
5. Determined refund amount: 128,000 RMB (80% of the 160,000 RMB core gift).

Structure of the verdict:
- 【本院认为】 (Reasoning): Cite Article 5, explain the lack of registration, acknowledge the 160,000 RMB gift, explain the 80% calculation (balancing short cohabitation vs. pregnancy termination/expenses), and dismiss the 'tea money' claim.
